                    < p class="about__description">In the heart of the Pacific Ocean, there existed a unique organization known as the Kiwi Oceanic Group. This group was a coalition of passionate New Zealanders dedicated to protecting the vast and vibrant marine ecosystems of the Pacific.</p>
